        <mxCell id="judge2" value="Judge B&#10;e.g. GPT-4o-mini" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#9673a6;dashed=1;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1150" y="855" width="140" height="45" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="legend" value="Orange = deterministic discriminator engine (questions come from the catalog)&#10;Purple = verification layers (programmatic guardrail + multi-LLM panel)&#10;Guided mode runs end-to-end with zero LLM keys; free-form needs a provider key&#10;Explanation cache (app.explanation_cache): writer + panel run once per outcome bucket (profile answers × policy versions, content-hashed); later users in the bucket are served the verified result with zero LLM calls&#10;LLM_ECONOMY ladder: full → lean (skip panel) → deterministic (zero LLM: template reasons from verified fields; mode is part of the cache key)&#10;Spend ledger (app.llm_usage): every LLM call metered by day/model/role, cache hits as zero-token rows; GET /ops/usage; DAILY_TOKEN_BUDGET warns once/day" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;size=14;align=left;spacing=6;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1150" y="990" width="300" height="95" as="geometry" />
